	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I just tried playing Sword of Hope on Gameboy and got a big surprise at the first battle.  The bgm was ripped from level 60 of Snoopy's Magic Show.  Any more examples of music recycled across unrelated games?  There's also the sound fx from Bart vs. the Space Mutants used in Home Alone 2 and Swamp Thing.  *ick*

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


