		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My favorite was "Erika to Satoru no Yumebouken" (Track #24).  It's straight out of Karate Kid.  So here's a game using mostly expansion sound, then suddenly you press Next Track, and hear Karate Kid!

		

